metadata.name: TapeHeads #1
metadata.description: TapeHeads are a collection of 10k cassette tape enthusiasts who love music. Join the TapeHeads community with your own unique TapeHead. Each Tapeheads NFT gives you access to TapeHeads Land on Sandbox, voting rights on the development of the music metaverse, cost-free rental on TapeHeads Land for events, exclusive Sandbox TapeHeads avatars for early adopters, limited and rare merchandise, and other benefits. Visit http://www.tapeheads.io for more information!
metadata.creator: ProtoHeads.io
